narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, if you're interested in graphic design or how information is visually communicated culturally, take it.
I would highly recommend it to anyone who is interested in pursuing design or visual communication as a future career.

Yes! Both Julian and Doug are absolutely amazing. The two assignments (a timeline in Doug's half and a book in Julian's) were a lot of work, but very gratifying. It was nice tofinally get a foundation of the history of design in the first half of the course.
